__NOTOC__
The appearance of the tree can be changed in the configuration file <tt>LocalSettings.php</tt>. After including the Semantic Treeview extension, you can choose whether the tree should be rendered using dotted lines (by default set to <tt>false</tt>). In addition, you can select the icons to be used in the tree by specifying the variable <tt>$wgTreeViewImages</tt> for various tree elements.
<pre>
$wgTreeViewShowLines = true;
$wgTreeViewImages['folder'] = "<imagepath>"; // (e.g., "$wgScriptPath/images/0/05/folder.gif")
</pre>
