For example, by using the following configuration, the SMW+ manual tree would be rendered as follows:
<pre>
require_once('extensions/Treeview/Treeview.php');
$wgTreeViewImages['root'] = "$wgScriptPath/images/e/e1/Eclipse_root.png";
$wgTreeViewImages['folder'] = "$wgScriptPath/images/7/7b/Eclipse_folder.png";
$wgTreeViewImages['folderOpen'] = "$wgScriptPath/images/7/7b/Eclipse_folder.png";
$wgTreeViewImages['node'] = "$wgScriptPath/images/e/eb/Eclipse_leaf.png";
$wgTreeViewShowLines = true;
</pre>

